# Cypress E2E Test Project

This project contains automated end-to-end tests using the Cypress framework.

## Requirements

- Node.js (recommended version: 16 or higher)
- NPM (automatically included with Node.js)

## Installation and Running

1.  Clone the repository:

    git clone https://github.com/RichardDolinsky/projekt-cypress-july.git
    cd "Path to your cloned repository folder"

2. Install dependencies:
       npm install

2.  Run using Cypress UI:
    npx cypress open

    or to run a specific test directly:
    npx cypress run --spec "cypress/e2e/sauceDemo/first.cy.ts"
